{"tid":1002432,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打台灣工作緊?","createTime":"2019-01-31T02:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T11:24:04.000Z","uid":58609,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c06c50ec6c796b11fd67bf42aa8f6f4dcb983a","tid":1002432,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:43:03.000Z","msg":"喺台北做左半年.人工比香港少左少但物價比香港低好多.衣食住行都平(只要唔係入口野).<br />\n但生活質素好.<br />\n係呢度先感受到咩叫生活,喺香港叫生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n空間呢點香港永遠超越唔到台灣,無論住定係出去玩,唔洗逼就係爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有就係少蝗(除非你覺得台灣人係繁體蝗)<br />\n有冇巴打都喺台北做野?"},{"pid":"82ac71adde80379ce5d95564d4149038d2f8a0ff","tid":1002432,"uid":652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:44:04.000Z","msg":"食唔食到台妹😂😂😂"},{"pid":"eaefe333163ea63802b8fce48bcab6feb09a1e57","tid":1002432,"uid":88451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58bee51b247661e0c4d6515598986017dbb4b926","tid":1002432,"uid":191919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dcd6cd0635adb09eda3f3da051794a380181acf","tid":1002432,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ac71adde80379ce5d95564d4149038d2f8a0ff","tid":1002432,"uid":652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:44:04.000Z","msg":"食唔食到台妹😂😂😂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:07:26.000Z","msg":"未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fe38bbafc4c85a0ff415f14b17856f9453144d","tid":1002432,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaefe333163ea63802b8fce48bcab6feb09a1e57","tid":1002432,"uid":88451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:08:46.000Z","msg":"it行業，香港有分公司"},{"pid":"df501c9ae648d5786da2fa0c